modName: IMMAD'S More Riverwood Trees - Environment Mod
summary: This mod adds more trees to Riverwood , to make it look better .
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds more trees to Riverwood , to make it look better . There are trees in water too !!
With this mod , Riverwood , become RiverWOOD :D ! This mod is compatible with : "Riverwood Redux" by X2ash .

-Tested by me on :
------------------------------------------------------
[color=#FF0000]PC CONFIGURATION[/color]
------------------------------------------------------
Intel Core i7 2600 4.41 GHz
Gainward Phantom GTX760 4 Gb
8 Gb Ram
------------------------------------------------------
[color=#FF0000]SKYRIM CONFIGURATION[/color]
------------------------------------------------------
All setting to ULTRA
Antialiasing 8x
Anisotropic Filter 16x
------------------------------------------------------
[color=#FF0000]INSTALLATION[/color]
------------------------------------------------------
MANUAL : Installation is very simple ! Just drag an drop "More Riverwood Trees.esp" into your "Data" folder !
NMM : If you receive error : "boss_api_error_file_not_found" don't mind . You can found "More Riverwood Trees.esp" in "Plugins" tab
